messaging.subject: Diabetes Management Introduction
messaging.message: The results from your recent health screening indicate your A1C is above 6.5%.  An A1C test estimates your average blood sugar levels over the past three months, and a value above 6.5% is considered diabetic. This is something we can work on together to ensure you live a long, healthy life...

messaging.subject: Biometric Screening Results
messaging.message: Guess what, Judy? Your biometric results are in, and you just earned 500 points!

messaging.subject: You Just Earned 500 Points: See Your Results
messaging.message: Hi Judy, Nice work completing your biometric test! This important screening can detect conditions early - before they become big health problems - and early detection can lead to a healthier, longer life.

messaging.subject: Make this a new you new year!
messaging.message: Five simple ways to help you shed those post-holiday pounds that actually work: Drink Water, Especially Before Meals. ... Eat Eggs For Breakfast. ... Drink Coffee (Preferably Black) ... Drink Green Tea. ... Cook With Coconut Oil ...

messaging.subject: Log In Today and Start Earning Points
messaging.message: Let's get started! Log in now to start your journey to becoming a healthier you. It's so simple, we've created custom programs just for you...
